JqueryInPlaceEditing
====================

JQuery style in place editing plugin. This plugin was last tested with jquery-1.6.


How to use
=======
Step 1: Include the following javascript tags.

<script type="text/javascript" src="jquery-1.6.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="jquery.in_place_editing.js"></script>

Step 2: Use it!

$(document).ready(function() {
    // without a handle
    $(".editable1").in_place_editing();

    // with a handle
    $(".editable2").in_place_editing({handleImage:"leaf.png"})
});

You should now be able to edit all objects of class 'editable' in place. Enjoy!

	

